+|   I32 |         I32 |    2^27      |       57 |             216 |      block |    672x | 51.97% |
+|   I32 |         I32 |    2^27      |       57 |              18 |       warp |   2832x | 86.45% |
+|   I64 |         I32 |    2^27      |       57 |             216 |      block |    720x | 76.07% |
+|   I64 |         I32 |    2^27      |       57 |              18 |       warp |    784x | 86.95% |
